{"id":15282,"date":"2024-04-25T03:23:59","date_gmt":"2024-04-25T03:23:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sultan@brandsolutions.icu"},"modified":"2025-08-20T05:55:51","modified_gmt":"2025-08-20T05:55:51","password":"","slug":"overview","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/documentation\/introduction\/overview\/","title":{"rendered":"Overview"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"Welcome-to-6Valley\"><strong>6Valley &#8211; Your All-in-One Multi-Vendor eCommerce CMS<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>6Valley is a powerful, feature-rich Multi-Vendor eCommerce CMS designed to help you build, manage, and scale your online marketplace with ease. Whether you want to manage multiple independent vendors or run your own in-house store, 6Valley offers the flexibility to operate locally or expand globally.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of 6Valley&#8217;s standout features is its adaptability \u2014 you can seamlessly switch between multi-vendor and single-vendor modes at any time, giving you complete control over your business model. From selling physical goods to delivering digital products, 6Valley supports it all, with a seamless experience across web and mobile platforms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Highlights<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Multi-Vendor &amp; Single-Vendor Support<\/strong> \u2013 Switch between models effortlessly.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Comprehensive Product Support<\/strong> \u2013 Sell both physical and digital products.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Cross-Platform Availability<\/strong> \u2013 Fully functional on web, Android, and iOS.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Scalable &amp; Secure<\/strong> \u2013 Built with modern, reliable technologies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Technologies Behind 6Valley<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong><strong>Solution \/ Module<\/strong><\/strong><\/td><td><strong><strong>Technology<\/strong><\/strong><\/td><td><strong><strong>Key Features<\/strong><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Super Admin Panel<\/td><td>PHP Laravel<\/td><td>Role-based access, commission management, built-in POS, order &amp; delivery management, promotions, and in-house shop control.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Vendor Panel<\/td><td>PHP Laravel<\/td><td>Full vendor product management and sales tracking.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Website \/ Frontend<\/td><td>PHP Laravel&nbsp;<\/td><td>Fully responsive, cross-device compatibility.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Customer App<\/td><td>Flutter<\/td><td>Available on Android &amp; iOS for seamless shopping.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Deliveryman App<\/td><td>Flutter<\/td><td>Android &amp; iOS support for order delivery tracking.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Vendor App<\/td><td>Flutter<\/td><td>Android &amp; iOS access for vendor operations.<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>6Valley &#8211; Your All-in-One Multi-Vendor eCommerce CMS 6Valley is a powerful, feature-rich Multi-Vendor eCommerce CMS designed to help you build, manage, and scale your online marketplace with ease. Whether you want to manage multiple independent vendors or run your own in-house store, 6Valley offers the flexibility to operate locally or expand globally. One of 6Valley&#8217;s &#8230; <a title=\"Overview\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/documentation\/introduction\/overview\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about Overview\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"doc_category":[198],"doc_tag":[203],"class_list":["post-15282","docs","type-docs","status-publish","hentry","doc_category-introduction","doc_tag-overview"],"year_month":"2025-11","word_count":203,"total_views":0,"reactions":{"happy":0,"normal":0,"sad":0},"author_info":{"name":"Sunny Sultan","author_nicename":"sultan6amtech-com","author_url":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/author\/sultan6am